profile:
Hello Niagara Region

Anthony Hauls Junk is a full-service junk removal that specializes in garage cleanouts, tenant cleanouts, appliance removal and minor construction cleanouts.  During this period due to COVID ALL JUNK MUST BE OUTSIDE OR IN THE GARAGE. As for tenant cleanouts, no one can be in the residence while junk is being removed.

Pictures of junk removal jobs gives me a idea of the job required. Sometimes I'm even able to give a quote before seeing the job. To give the best quotes possible, I can't stress this enough: have all your junk in one place. It makes the job less labour intensive and will save you money. 

I also provide appliance pick up.  Rates are: L shaped sofas, recliner couches, three seated sofas, fridges and freezer chests $100. Anything smaller these items will cost $60

I look forward to working with you in the future. Please see the pictures of my completed jobs. Contactless pay can be achieved through e-transfers.



Thanks, Niagara Region!
